lead_paragraph: The Marlins have begun the painful task of revamping their rotation following the death of ace Jose Fernandez, reaching a deal with free agent Edinson Volquez.

headline.print_headline: AP Source: Volquez, Marlins Agree to $22M, 2-Year Deal
